1. Create a raw BMP (Non-Rle) - 244 Color 640x480  - Bootlogo_244.bmp
2. Convert BMP to PPM
	   bmptoppm Bootlogo_244.bmp > Bootlogo_244.ppm.bin
3. Convert to PPM ASCII Format
		pnmnoraw Bootlogo_244.ppm.bin > Bootlogo.ppm

Alternatively if you create a image > 244 colors (from step 1 and 2) you
need to reduce the image to 244 color using 
   	ppmquant Bootlogo_hi.ppm > Bootlogo_224.ppm  					